Networking final project - Gretchen Knuth, Yoyi Liao

To run this program you need to run `pip install cryptography`

Then you can run TCPServer and TCPClient on separate terminals/devices. Make sure to update the IP address and port number on each file to reflect your current environment.

To broadcast a message, just type whatever the message is and send it.

To send a direct message, add `@target ` before your message, where `target` is the username of another client connected to the server.